zie Chapstick》和《Living In The 20s》。</p><p>在最近的一次采访中，该乐队解释说， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/green-day-say-new-album-saviors-bridges-gap-between-dookie-and-american-idiot-best-of-their-career-3546641">《Saviors》“弥合了”粉丝最喜爱的唱片《American Idiot》和《Dookie》之间的差距</a>。他们还将该项目描述为他们职业生涯中“最好的”。</p><p> Green Day 将于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/green-day-announce-2024-saviors-stadium-tour-including-huge-london-show-buy-tickets-3529041">明年开始大规模的世界巡演以支持这张专辑</a>，同时庆祝 1994 年的《Dookie》发行 30 周年和 2004 年的《American Idiot》发行 20 周年。此次演出包括在伦敦温布利体育场举行的一场大型演出。 <a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/green-day-tickets/artist/768353?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=xWpzsXyDbxyPRnUx98SctTxgUkFQv%3ATlnUsmUU0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此查找英国和爱尔兰日期的所有剩余门票</a>。</p><p>此外，三人组合将于明年夏天与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pet-shop-boys">Pet Shop Boys</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-prodigy">The Prodigy</a>一起<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/green-day-pet-shop-boys-and-the-prodigy-to-headline-isle-of-wight-festival-2024-lineup-buy-tickets-3528939#:~:text=Prodigy%20to%20headline-,Green%20Day%2C%20Pet%20Shop%20Boys%20and%20The%20Prodigy%20to,Isle%20Of%20Wight%20Festival%202024&amp;text=Isle%20Of%20Wight%20Festival%20has,Newport%20between%20June%2020%2D23.">成为 2024 年怀特岛音乐节的主角</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/green-day-release-new-single-dilemma-listen-watch-video-3555305">聆听 Green Day 的“个人”新单曲“Dilemma”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
